OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781014279
OL,3,CWoman, 19, dies after gunshots heard
OL,4,Ccoming from house in North London
OL,6,FA 19-year-old woman has died after
OL,7,Fgunshots were heard at a house in
OL,8,Fnorth London, police said.
OL,10,FParamedics called police to the home
OL,11,Fin Dale Grove, Finchley, at 12.15am on
OL,12,FMonday and the victim, whose family
OL,13,Fhas been told, was pronounced dead at
OL,14,Fthe scene.
OL,16,FA murder investigation has been
OL,17,Flaunched and a post-mortem examination
OL,18,Fwill be carried out, the Metropolitan
OL,19,FPolice said.
