OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781014279
OL,3,CWoman, 19, dies after gunshots heard
OL,4,Ccoming from house in North London
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Allam
OL,7,FBhangoo said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,8,Fthe young woman's family at this
OL,9,Fincredibly difficult time as they
OL,10,Fbegin to come to terms with their loss.
OL,12,F"We understand the concern this
OL,13,Fincident will cause within the
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,F"While our inquiries are ongoing,
OL,17,Fresidents can expect to see an
OL,18,Fincreased police presence over the
OL,19,Fcoming days, and I encourage anyone
OL,20,Fwith concerns to speak with officers.
