OL,3,CWoman, 19, dies after gunshots heard
OL,4,Ccoming from house in North London
OL,6,FAnyone with information about the
OL,7,Fincident or doorbell or dashcam
OL,8,Ffootage from around midnight in or
OL,9,Fnear to Dale Grove is asked to contact
OL,10,Fpolice via 101, quoting reference 34/
OL,11,F8JUN, or anonymously through
OL,12,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555 111.
